                <note rend="inline" type="source">842.24/245</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">President</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-08-13">August 13,
                            1943</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p rend="center">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Memorandum for the President</hi>
                </p>
                <p>Reference is made to Mr. Early’s memorandum of August 11 transmitting a
                    memorandum dated August 3 from Mr. Lauchlin Currie in regard to a proposed
                    statement concerning the Joint War Aid Committee, United States–Canada.</p>
                <p>The proposed statement quoted in Mr. Early’s memorandum is satisfactory to the
                    Department of State.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>C[<hi rend="smallcaps">ordell</hi>] H[<hi rend="smallcaps"
                        >ull</hi>]</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
